title: Weirdhouse Cinema: Alice (1988)
itunes:title: Weirdhouse Cinema: Alice (1988)
description:
In this episode of Weirdhouse Cinema, Rob and guest co-host Seth discuss the 1988 surrealist dark fantasy film “Alice” by Czech stop-motion animation master Jan Švankmajer.
